ZH: 这个政府的腐败问题已经引起了广泛关注。
EN: The issue of corruption in this government has attracted widespread attention.

ZH: 这是一个腐败的行为，不能容忍。
EN: This is a corrupt behavior that cannot be tolerated.

ZH: 媒体曝光了公司高管的腐败行为。
EN: The media exposed the corrupt behavior of the company's executives.

ZH: 这些丑闻揭露了政府内部的腐败问题。
EN: These scandals exposed the corruption within the government.

ZH: 他因为腐败被判处长达十年的监禁。
EN: He was sentenced to ten years in prison for corruption.

ZH: 腐败行为对社会造成了严重危害。
EN: Corruption has caused serious harm to society.

ZH: 我们必须严惩腐败现象，否则社会将无法正常运转。
EN: We must crack down on corruption, or else society will not function properly.

ZH: 这个国家的腐败问题已经严重到无法挽回的地步。
EN: The corruption problem in this country has reached a point of no return.

ZH: 他因为腐败被解除了职务。
EN: He was dismissed from his position because of corruption.

ZH: 他的腐败行为导致了公司的破产。
EN: His corrupt behavior led to the bankruptcy of the company.

ZH: 那个官员已经因为腐败问题被停职调查。
EN: That official has been suspended pending investigation into corruption.

ZH: 这个机构已经实施了一系列措施来打击腐败。
EN: This institution has implemented a series of measures to combat corruption.

ZH: 政府应该采取更严厉的手段来打击腐败。
EN: The government should take tougher measures to fight corruption.

ZH: 我们不能让腐败蔓延下去。
EN: We cannot allow corruption to spread.

ZH: 他因为揭露腐败问题而被迫流亡国外。
EN: He was forced to flee the country for exposing corruption.

ZH: 那个国家的腐败情况严重到了让人发指的程度。
EN: The level of corruption in that country is outrageous.

ZH: 腐败已经成为了这个行业的固有问题。
EN: Corruption has become an inherent problem in this industry.

ZH: 那个高官被指控参与了腐败活动。
EN: That high-ranking official has been accused of involvement in corrupt activities.

ZH: 腐败是导致这个组织衰败的根本原因。
EN: Corruption is the root cause of the decline of this organization.

ZH: 现在是时候根除这个国家内部的腐败了。
EN: It is time to eradicate the corruption within this country.
